---

Third-party agent code bundled in agents/external/ was originally published
as public Kaggle notebooks by their respective authors. Each agent folder
retains the author's original agent.yaml (with author + kernel_slug credit)
and is included here for local benchmarking convenience.

Credits:
- agents/external/pilkwang-structured  — Pilkwang Kim (Apache 2.0)
- agents/external/tamrazov-starwars    — Roman Tamrazov
- agents/external/sigmaborov-starter   — sigmaborov
- agents/external/sigmaborov-reinforce — sigmaborov
- agents/external/yuriygreben-architect — yuriygreben
- agents/external/kashiwaba-rl         — YumeNeko / kashiwaba

If you are the author of one of these agents and want it removed, please open
a GitHub issue.
